Name: Vacation Adventures: Park Ranger 14
About the game: Help run Pinecreek Hills National Park Have fun organizing Summer Season events on Bluewaters Lake, Cherokee River & Apache Nature trails. Learn about Wildlife. Camp & Picnic beside Rivers and Bayous. Explore atmospheric Waterfalls, Gorges, enchanted Caves and beautiful outdoor locations. Have fun hiking, biking and riding Pinecreek’s new Rail-Bike Trail. Present Springfield’s Community & Good Neighbor awards. Have Campfires & BBQ’s. Spot Bears, Deer and Eagles. Play great Hogs & Puzzles, Spot 100’s of Animals, Birds, Fish and Wildlife. Protect the environment, get Souvenirs and Awards along the way. Play great Hogs & Puzzles, Spot 100’s of Animals, Birds, Fish and Wildlife.
